    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A and B: Dorsolateral and ventral views of the adult male holotype SYS a 002169 of Xenophrys insularis sp. nov. in life; C and D: Ventral views of hand and foot of the holotype in life; E and F: Dorsolateral and ventral views of the adult female paratype SYS a 002168 in life." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/998488/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.998490>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A, B and C: Dorsal, ventral and lateral views of the adult male holotype SYS a 002169 of Xenophrys insularis sp. nov. in preservative; D: Front view of head the holotype in preservative; E and F: Ventral views of hand and foot of the holotype in preservative." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/998490/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.998484>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Sampling localities of Xenophrys toads in this study. 1: Nan’ao Island, Guangdong; 2: Hong Kong; 3: Heishiding Nature Reserve, Guangdong; 4: Mt. Longtou, Guangdong; 5: Nanfengmian Nature Reserve, Hunan; 6: Mt. Jinggang, Jiangxi; 7: Taoyuandong Nature Reserve, Hunan; 8: Guadun Village (= Kuatun), Fujian; 9: Mt. huangshan, Anhui; 10: Dujiangyan City, Sichuan." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/998484/files/figure.png" ;
